videos.headline: Ball State WR Hall left wide open for 46-yard TD
videos.description: Ball State QB Drew Plitt slings one over the top to WR Justin Hall who takes it to the house for a 46-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Ball State WR Hall left wide open for 46-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ball State QB sneaks for TD, converts 2-point conversion
videos.description: Ball State QB Drew Plitt sneaks into the end zone for a touchdown and then passes to Riley Miller for a two-point conversion.
